  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s</span><span class=\"text-danger\">]</span></strong> in half</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl &ndash; this is your <strong>harissa marinade</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cut the<strong> chicken thigh fillets</strong> into strips, add them to the <strong>harissa marinade</strong> and mix well</p>\r\n<p>Thread the <strong>chicken strips</strong> evenly onto each <strong>skewer</strong> and pop them in the fridge until later</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
